# Competitor Monitor - Environment Variables

# Required: Claude API for AI agent
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# Recommended: Firecrawl API for web scraping (handles JS-heavy sites)
# Get from: https://firecrawl.dev
FIRECRAWL_API_KEY=fc-...

# Optional: SMTP settings (only needed if email delivery is enabled)
# Example: Gmail SMTP
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=your-email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=your-app-specific-password
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@yourcompany.com

# Notes:
# - For Gmail: Use app-specific password, not regular password
# - For other providers: Check their SMTP documentation
# - If FIRECRAWL_API_KEY is not set, system falls back to HTTP + BeautifulSoup (no JS support)
